label: Install
title: Steps to Install
---


Follow the instructions to install Tailwind and Flowbite from this link: https://flowbite.com/docs/getting-started/rails/

after

install Fluxbit gem

install Fluxbit js package (from npm)

add this to tailwind.config.js:

```javascript
  const execSync = require('child_process').execSync;
  module.exports.content.push(
    `${execSync("bundle show fluxbit").toString().trim()}/**/*.{erb,html,rb}`
  );
```